com.github.protobufel.el

Class BeanELResolverEx

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.el.ELResolver
      • javax.el.BeanELResolver
        • com.github.protobufel.el.BeanELResolverEx

  • public class BeanELResolverEx
extends javax.el.BeanELResolver
    A BeanELResolver with advanced handling of the bean's overloaded methods. Consults with the base's BeanInfo, if present, to better handle overloading methods' ambiguity - the BeanInfo declared methods are in preference to the rest.
